title: Brahms - Liebeslieder Walzer - Mathis, Fassbaender, et al
description:
Johannes Brahms: Liebeslieder Walzer, Opp. 52, 65, Drei Quartette, op.64.

Two sets of love songs for vocal quartet and two pianos, as well as Four Vocal Quartets, op. 64. The recording was released by DG in 1983. The all-star personnel for this lovely recording are as follows:

Edith Mathis, soprano
Brigitte Fassbaender, alto
Peter Schreier, tenor
Dietrich Fischer-Dieskau, baritone
Karl Engel and Wolfgang Sawallisch, pianos

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
